N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 153.7 - Tonnage reports

State Regulations

In accord with section 146-c of the law, each licensee who
distributes commercial fertilizer in this State shall furnish the commissioner
with a written report for the period January 1st through December 31st of each
year indicating the tonnage distributed during that period on forms or in a
format prescribed by the commissioner. Said report shall be filed within 30
days of the end of the reporting period. Notes
